name: Stood Up
description:
You know that feeling of waiting around for someone, full of hope, dreams and promise. Only they never turn up....  Getting stood up is hard.  Makes you feel like you jut were not good enough to even be given a chance.  :(

MykNash (CAPT S.S.-WAGMI) (Crow's Nest CREW, S-FL)@myknash and Oopsy Owl both found out just how that feels during the #blinddate event.  However, they got set up for a speed date and boy did they have some fun!  :)  We were good enough, we just had to wait for the right partner!

Hope you like our project!
